title: Dell Inspiron 15R 5521 Windows 8 x64 Recovery Disks
description:
This is the full recovery disk set for Dell 15R 5521. These disks will fully restore all software originally installed on this model. This is Windows 8 x64. This will recreate all factory partitions as they were, including the recovery partition.

These are the recovery disks created when you first get the computer and contain no updates. 

There are different variations of these recovery disks and this may not contain all drivers or software shipped with your particular model. Your laptop should have came from the factory with Windows 8 for this to activate properly.

This should also work on similar models
